import Vue from 'vue'
import { Button, FormModel, 
  Input, Icon, message,
   Layout, Menu, Card, Table, Row, Col, ConfigProvider, Modal, Pagination, Select} from 'ant-design-vue'

message.config({
    top: `100px`,
    duration: 2,
    maxCount: 3,
  });

Vue.prototype.$message = message
Vue.prototype.$confirm = Modal.confirm

Vue.use(Button)
Vue.use(FormModel)
Vue.use(Input)
Vue.use(Icon)
Vue.use(Layout)
Vue.use(Menu)
Vue.use(Card)
Vue.use(Table)
Vue.use(Row)
Vue.use(Col)
Vue.use(ConfigProvider)
Vue.use(Pagination)
Vue.use(Modal)
